properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Port Aransas to Matagorda Ship Channel out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20 NM
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 16 at 12:03PM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
Moist onshore flow will continue to produce fog along the
nearshore waters and coastal areas this afternoon and evening.
Visibilities will generally range from 3 to 5 nautical miles,
with patchy dense fog of 1 nautical mile or less at times. Areas
of dense fog may redevelop tonight.

Mariners over the Bay Waters and over the Nearshore Coastal
Waters within 20 nautical miles offshore are urged to prepare for
rapidly changing visibilities.

NWSheadline: PATCHY DENSE FOG THIS AFTERNOON AND EVENING FOR THE NEARSHORE WATERS
